Ajara Nchout Njoya (amụrụ na 12 Jenụwarị na afọ 1993) bụ onye Cameroon ọkachamara na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-agbachitere Serie A club Inter Milan na ndị otu ụmụ nwanyị Cameroon.
A mụrụ ya na Njissé, Foumban, Nchout kwuru na ezinụlọ ya kụdara ya ume ịgba bọọlụ, na-ahọrọ ka ọ lekwasị anya na agụmakwụkwọ.
Na Jenụwarị na afọ 2015 Nchout kwetara isonyere Western New York Flash nke NWSL. Ọ gbara bọọlụ na Russian Top Division maka FC Energy Voronezh na WFC Rossiyanka.
Flash hapụrụ ya n'ọnwa Ọktoba afọ 2015
N'ọnwa Disemba afọ 2015, ọ mara ọkwa na ọ bịanyere aka na Sundsvalls DFF nke Swedish Elitettan.
Nchout mechara bịanye aka na Vålerenga mgbe ọ pụtara na egwuregwu 22 maka Sandviken
Ọ hapụrụ asọmpi ikpeazụ nke iko Norway na Sandviken ka ọ na-arụ ọrụ mba ụwa na Cameroon, egwuregwu ha meriri.
Dị ka onye otu egwuregwu mba Cameroon, ọ gbara bọọlụ na afọ 2012 Summer Olympics. Ọ bụkwa otu n'ime ndị otu mba na 2015 FIFA Women's World Cup na 2019 FIFA Women't World Cup
E mechiri ya maka egwuregwu anọ niile na afọ 2015 World Cup, wee gbaa goolu megide Japan,  ndị otu ahụ mechara bụrụ nke abụọ na asọmpi ahụ

N'oge 2019 World Cup, ọ gbara naanị goolu abụọ nke otu ahụ na naanị mmeri nke otu ahụ nke egwuregwu otu nke dugara ha na agba nke iri na isii. N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ, na afọ 2019, a họpụtara ya maka afọ 2019 FIFA Puskas Award maka ihe mgbaru ọsọ ya megide New Zealand na FIFA Women's World Cup
